tool_description:
This endpoint allows you to retrieve the latest results of the Aviator game on the Aposta Ganha ( apostaganha.bet )  platform.  

You can access the array containing the most recent results of the Aviator game. 

Each element of the array represents the numerical value of the result obtained in the game, with the first element being the most recent and the last being the oldest.   

This endpoint can be integrated into other applications to provide up-to-date information on the results of the...
name: Aposta Ganha Aviator API
title: Aposta Ganha Aviator API

api_list.name: apostaganha-aviator-latest
api_list.description:
Will retrieve the latest results from Aviator at Aposta Ganha.

- The first result is the most recent
- The last result is the oldest
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://aposta-ganha-aviator-api1.p.rapidapi.com/apostaganha-aviator-latest"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "aposta-ganha-aviator-api1.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
